**Basic intution**
this question is somewhat similar to longest common subsequence which is a very popular dp problem. Here were are selecting last character of s3 and comparing it with  last element of s1 and s2.

**Example1**
   consider s1="abc",s2="adg" and s3="aabcdg"
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/fc54b5d6-67c8-451e-af04-0903dc4809ce_1622638700.4142802.png)

**Example2**
