To me this is a very typical DP problem, so my initial approach was an O(n) DP solution as below, but it failed with LTE:
```
int integerReplacement(int n) {
        int dp[n + 1]; memset(dp, 0, sizeof(dp));
        for (int i = 2; i <= n; i++) {
