Everything is given in the problem description, just implement the **recursive function** and Memoize the code, to avoid TLE.
# Complexity
- Time complexity:O(Log(N))
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity:O(N)
