Steps :
1. if n is even , Simply divide it by 2
2. if n is odd ,  we have to replace it by either n+1 or n-1 , which results in minimum number of operation. To decide this check which one of the following  (n+1)/2 or (n-1)/2 results in even number , replace it by that operation.

**Example :**

3 -> 2 ->1 , ans  = 2
4 -> 2 ->1 , ans = 2
10 -> 5 ->4 ->2->1 , ans = 4
11 -> 12 -> 6 ->3 ->2 ->1 ,  ans = 5
50 -> 25 ->24 ->12 -> 6->3 ->2->1 , ans = 7

